{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01NWEgYS1qBYwzxDqYrswUnK","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→package org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pettype;\n     2→\n     3→import jakarta.ejb.EJB;\n     4→\n     5→import jakarta.ejb.Stateless;\n     6→import jakarta.ws.rs.GET;\n     7→import jakarta.ws.rs.Path;\n     8→import jakarta.ws.rs.PathParam;\n     9→import jakarta.ws.rs.Produces;\n    10→import jakarta.ws.rs.core.MediaType;\n    11→import lombok.extern.java.Log;\n    12→import org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pettype.api.PetTypeDto;\n    13→import org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pettype.api.PetTypeEndpointUtil;\n    14→import org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pettype.api.PetTypeListDto;\n    15→import org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pettype.db.PetTypeService;\n    16→\n    17→import java.io.Serializable;\n    18→import java.util.List;\n    19→\n    20→@Log\n    21→@Path(\"/petType\")\n    22→@Stateless\n    23→public class PetTypeEndpoint implements Serializable {\n    24→\n    25→    private static final long serialVersionUID = -105453087511255998L;\n    26→\n    27→    @EJB\n    28→    private PetTypeService petTypeService;\n    29→\n    30→    @EJB\n    31→    private PetTypeEndpointUtil petTypeEndpointUtil;\n    32→\n    33→    @GET\n    34→    @Path(\"/list\")\n    35→    @Produces(MediaType.APPLICATION_JSON)\n    36→    public List<PetTypeDto> getList() {\n    37→        log.info(\"getList\");\n    38→        return this.petTypeEndpointUtil.dtoListFactory(petTypeService.getAll()).getPetType();\n    39→    }\n    40→\n    41→    @GET\n    42→    @Path(\"/{id}\")\n    43→    @Produces(MediaType.APPLICATION_JSON)\n    44→    public PetTypeDto getEntity(@PathParam(\"id\") Long id) {\n    45→        log.info(\"getEntity\");\n    46→        return this.petTypeEndpointUtil.dtoFactory(petTypeService.findById(id));\n    47→    }\n    48→\n    49→    @GET\n    50→    @Path(\"/list+json\")\n    51→    @Produces(MediaType.APPLICATION_JSON)\n    52→    public List<PetTypeDto> getListAsJson() {\n    53→        log.info(\"getList\");\n    54→        return this.petTypeEndpointUtil.dtoListFactory(petTypeService.getAll()).getPetType();\n    55→    }\n    56→\n    57→    @GET\n    58→    @Path(\"/{id}+json\")\n    59→    @Produces(MediaType.APPLICATION_JSON)\n    60→    public PetTypeDto getEntityAsJson(@PathParam(\"id\") Long id) {\n    61→        log.info(\"getEntity\");\n    62→        return this.petTypeEndpointUtil.dtoFactory(petTypeService.findById(id));\n    63→    }\n    64→\n    65→    @GET\n    66→    @Path(\"/list+xml\")\n    67→    @Produces(MediaType.APPLICATION_XML)\n    68→    public PetTypeListDto getListAsXml() {\n    69→        log.info(\"getListAsXml\");\n    70→        return this.petTypeEndpointUtil.dtoListFactory(petTypeService.getAll());\n    71→    }\n    72→\n    73→    @GET\n    74→    @Path(\"/{id}+xml\")\n    75→    @Produces(MediaType.APPLICATION_XML)\n    76→    public PetTypeDto getEntityAsXml(@PathParam(\"id\") Long id) {\n    77→        log.info(\"getEntityAsXml\");\n    78→        return this.petTypeEndpointUtil.dtoFactory(petTypeService.findById(id));\n    79→    }\n    80→\n    81→}\n    82→\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01SVxxBDxeR7TyCQEsMaznkq","session_id":"f1542671-6929-49f9-9925-fcf6260de3ab","uuid":"f5ac325d-17d9-4b57-a7e2-f11fc0ea7b62"}
