{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01Jh71doojiU5PeFSxFNgPdf","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→package org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.specialty.db;\n     2→\n     3→import jakarta.ejb.EJB;\n     4→import jakarta.ejb.Stateless;\n     5→import lombok.extern.java.Log;\n     6→import org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.specialty.Specialty;\n     7→\n     8→import jakarta.annotation.PostConstruct;\n     9→import jakarta.annotation.PreDestroy;\n    10→\n    11→import java.util.List;\n    12→\n    13→@Log\n    14→@Stateless\n    15→public class SpecialtyServiceImpl implements SpecialtyService {\n    16→\n    17→    private static final long serialVersionUID = 6145428275502469961L;\n    18→\n    19→    @EJB\n    20→    private SpecialtyDao specialtyDao;\n    21→\n    22→    @Override\n    23→    public List<Specialty> getAll() {\n    24→        return this.specialtyDao.getAll();\n    25→    }\n    26→\n    27→    @Override\n    28→    public Specialty findById(long id) {\n    29→        log.info(\"findById Specialty: \" + id);\n    30→        return this.specialtyDao.findById(id);\n    31→    }\n    32→\n    33→    @Override\n    34→    public Specialty addNew(Specialty specialty) {\n    35→        log.info(\"addNew Specialty: \" + specialty.toString());\n    36→        return this.specialtyDao.addNew(specialty);\n    37→    }\n    38→\n    39→    @Override\n    40→    public Specialty update(Specialty specialty) {\n    41→        log.info(\"update Specialty: \" + specialty.toString());\n    42→        return this.specialtyDao.update(specialty);\n    43→    }\n    44→\n    45→    @Override\n    46→    public void delete(long id) {\n    47→        log.info(\"delete Specialty: \" + id);\n    48→        this.specialtyDao.delete(id);\n    49→    }\n    50→\n    51→    @Override\n    52→    public List<Specialty> search(String searchterm) {\n    53→        log.info(\"search Specialty: \" + searchterm);\n    54→        return this.specialtyDao.search(searchterm);\n    55→    }\n    56→\n    57→    @Override\n    58→    public void resetSearchIndex() {\n    59→        for(Specialty s:getAll()){\n    60→            this.specialtyDao.update(s);\n    61→        }\n    62→    }\n    63→\n    64→    @Override\n    65→    public Specialty findSpecialtyByName(String name) {\n    66→        return this.specialtyDao.findSpecialtyByName(name);\n    67→    }\n    68→\n    69→\n    70→    @PostConstruct\n    71→    public void postConstruct() {\n    72→        log.info(\"postConstruct: \"+SpecialtyServiceImpl.class.getSimpleName());\n    73→    }\n    74→\n    75→    @PreDestroy\n    76→    public void preDestroy() {\n    77→        log.info(\"preDestroy: \"+SpecialtyServiceImpl.class.getSimpleName());\n    78→    }\n    79→}\n    80→\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01SVxxBDxeR7TyCQEsMaznkq","session_id":"f1542671-6929-49f9-9925-fcf6260de3ab","uuid":"68cb3de4-346a-41fd-8726-084170149b34"}
