{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01QUqzY7DGv416gf4RXKgPHR","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"I now have a complete understanding of the application. Let me update my todo list and start the migration. This is a major Jakarta EE 10 application with:\n\n- **5 JPA entities**: Owner, Pet, PetType, Specialty, Vet, Visit\n- **EJB-based services**: `@Stateless` DAOs and Services with `@EJB` injection\n- **JAX-RS REST endpoints**: Using `@Path`, `@GET`, `@Produces`\n- **JSF/PrimeFaces UI**: XHTML templates, `@Named` backing beans\n- **CDI**: `@Inject`, `@SessionScoped`, `@ApplicationScoped`\n- **OpenLiberty runtime**: With PostgreSQL database\n\nMigration strategy: Convert to **Spring Boot 3.x** with:\n- Spring Data JPA (replacing manual EntityManager DAO layer)\n- Spring MVC REST controllers (replacing JAX-RS endpoints)\n- Spring DI (replacing CDI/EJB)\n- Thymeleaf or keep simple REST API (JSF UI is too complex to migrate; we'll focus on the REST API layer)\n- H2 database for simplicity (or keep PostgreSQL)"}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2178,"cache_read_input_tokens":99100,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":2178,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":748},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"f1542671-6929-49f9-9925-fcf6260de3ab","uuid":"9454c32c-51a1-4930-a868-24bf33255f59"}
