{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_014U7hkKpi7epiqW7en7pGeg","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.web.title=Jakarta EE 10 Petclinic\n     2→org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.web.copyright=2019-2023 Thomas W\\u00F6hlke\n     3→#\n     4→org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.home=Home\n     5→org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.home.welcome_a=First Steps\n     6→org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.home.welcome_a_a=add some Pet Types like dog,cat,mouse,...\n     7→org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.home.welcome_a_b=add some Specialties for Vetinarians like dentist, anesthetist, radiology,...\n     8→org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.home.welcome_a_c=add a Vetinarian\n     9→org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.home.welcome_a_d=add an Owner, add him am a Pet and his Pet a visit.\n    10→org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.home.welcome_info=More Info\n    11→org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.info=Information\n    12→org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.info.uml.DomainClassModell=Domain Class Modell\n    13→org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.info.uml.UseCases=Use Cases\n    14→org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.info.uml.UseCasesOwner=Use Cases Owner\n    15→org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.info.uml.UseCasesVet=Use Cases Vet\n    16→org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.info.uml.UseCasesSpecialty=Use Cases Specialty\n    17→org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.info.uml.UseCasesPetType=Use Cases PetType\n    18→org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.info.uml.UseCasesApplication=Use Cases Application\n    19→org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.user=User\n    20→org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.error=Fehler\n    21→org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.error.h2=An authentication failure occurred!\n    22→org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.error.p=The user name or password might be incorrect, or the user does not exist.\n    23→org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.start=Home\n    24→#\n    25→org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.list.showXml=View as XML\n    26→org.woehlke.jakartaee.pe